36% and the total expense ratio is</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399729635/image_1399729635.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742756-dubs-yield-boost-not-worth-return-cut", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 09:13:59"}, {"id": "4742753", "title": "Kymera: Protein Degradation Could Drive Dupixent-Like Value", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2178839740/image_2178839740.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Science, laboratory and teacher with students in classroom for learning, education and research at medical university. School, chemistry and woman with people for experiment, studying and teaching\" data-id=\"2178839740\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"810px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2178839740/image_2178839740.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2178839740/image_2178839740.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2178839740/image_2178839740.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2178839740/image_2178839740.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2178839740/image_2178839740.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2178839740/image_2178839740.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2178839740/image_2178839740.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2178839740/image_2178839740.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Jacob Wackerhausen/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong>Kymera Therapeutics</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/KYMR\" title=\"Kymera Therapeutics, Inc.\">KYMR</a></span>) is in the process of developing IRAK4 protein degrader KT-474 [SAR444656], with partner <strong>Sanofi</strong> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SNY\" title=\"Sanofi\">SNY</a>), in phase 2 clinical studies. That is, it is in the process of being investigated in two phase 2b</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2178839740/image_2178839740.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742753-kymera-protein-degradation-could-drive-dupixent-like-value", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 09:07:59"}, {"id": "4742752", "title": "Universal Health Realty: 7.3% Yield With 27 Years Of Hikes", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1166090290/image_1166090290.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Doctor with a digital tablet walking through hospital corridor\" data-id=\"1166090290\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1166090290/image_1166090290.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1166090290/image_1166090290.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1166090290/image_1166090290.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1166090290/image_1166090290.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1166090290/image_1166090290.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1166090290/image_1166090290.jpg?io=getty-